name: Branci Black Aluminum Full-Length Floor Mirror
details: Large, full-length floor mirror by fashion designer turned interior designer Brett Beldock is as sophisticated as it is timeless. Cast aluminum frame sports carved detailing throughout, with dramatic scallops and curves that bring warmth and organic texture to the piece.
